      "description": "**基于 Loki 日志的告警**：当某服务出现 `level=\"error\"` 的日志时触发告警。\n\n**日志格式要求**：JSON 行必须包含 `service` 和 `level` 字段，例如：\n```json\n{\"ts\": \"...\", \"level\": \"error\", \"msg\": \"...\", \"service\": \"draw-spec-box\"}\n```\n\n**修改告警**：编辑 `docker/grafana/resources/alerting/log_error_rule.json`",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": { "content": "", "mode": "markdown" },
      "title": "使用说明",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "tracelogkit-loki" },
      "description": "各服务的日志错误率（level=error 的日志占比）。",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 1 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 5 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true },
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "none" }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * ((sum by (service) (count_over_time({project=~\".+\"} | json | level=\"error\" [1m])) or on(service) (sum by (service) (count_over_time({project=~\".+\"} | json [1m])) * 0)) / sum by (service) (count_over_time({project=~\".+\"} | json [1m])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "日志错误率 (%) - 按 service",
